ActParliament of Canada Act
SubjectJames Rajotte ** MP Travel **
PrecisOrder authorizing Mr. JAMES RAJOTTE, Member of Parliament, to travel to CHICAGO, ILLINOIS, UNITED STATES, from April 22 to 23, 2012, to take part in a panel discussion at the Sixth Annual Financial Literacy and Education Summit on behalf of the Minister of Finance.
